@node Sec "Mightgosoft« UndocumentedFeature« | ®Mightgosoft 19100"
@prev "Sec"
@next "Sec"

Hey! you're not supposed to get here ;)
Go stand in the corner! 8-D


'Secret project'
Name:             BetterDCF
Status:           Internal Beta
Why not released: Incomplete (just a daemon and test util)
Plusses:
Ę Extremely simple reciever design (less parts & cheaper than any other
   DCF project on the AmiNet!)
Ę Connects to Joystick port (with tru-port!, Joystick transparant,
   can be switched off for CD32 joypads)
Ę Extremely low system overhead (0.36% for 68000, <0.0005% for '060!!!)
Ę Automatic DST/timezone setting + Battery clock sync. (if present)
Ę More than 3 years in development
Ę Stable like a rock, main routines written in Assembly
Ę 680x0 binary size : 9888 bytes

@{"" link MSec}
